rComments: Soil & Vegetation is actually a biogeography course - this is his first year teaching it and the course's name will be changed next year. I was disappointed about how little the class focused on soil & vegetation but it is a fun course - we analyze pollen under microscopes and have 2 assignments, a midterm, a paper worth 30% n final exam
